{"_id":"H1BT1RcEG","title":"6 - Using Foreman","body":{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"ag6qs","text":"6 - Using Foreman","type":"header-one","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"br96b","text":" You will need to restart server any time we make changes to the server.js file. Fortunately for us, we installed nodemon earlier which will restart the server any time we make changes to the file. While we are at it, we will set up Foreman to run both the server.js file and the React app at the same time ( which we were previously using `npm run start` for ). ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":65,"length":9,"style":"ITALIC"},{"offset":257,"length":9,"style":"ITALIC"},{"offset":114,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"},{"offset":233,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a8dtk","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7vle9","text":" Lets create a Procfile in our root directory, which Foreman will use to determine which commands to run. ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":15,"length":8,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"59kd9","text":" ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"14fb","text":"//Procfile\nweb: react-scripts start\napi: nodemon server.js","type":"custom-code-block-javascript","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9uesg","text":" And now head in to the package.json file to add a start-dev script: ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":24,"length":12,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"eis02","text":" ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7qjuq","text":"//package.json\n//…\n \"start\": \"react-scripts start\",\n \"start-dev\": \"nf start -p 3000\",\n//…","type":"custom-code-block-json","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cb62k","text":" Now when we ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"22ckd","text":"npm run start-dev","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},"dateCreated":"2018-01-16T01:05:01.238Z","lastUpdated":"2018-01-16T01:11:18.571Z","notebookId":"rygwluD4G"}
